Package: oxyQ
Title: Quality checking sample data for oxygenation plant monitoring
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Bart", "Huntley", , "Bart.Huntley@DBCA.wa.gov.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9519-4105"))
Description: This package contains a collection of functions to aid quality assessment 
    of raw sonde data. It does this by quality flagging measurements by way of  
    predetermined 'rules'. The package may expand to include additional functions 
    to aid in the assessment of oxygenation plant function.
